data.description: This beautiful horse property is located near the Poetry area and features a cozy 3 bdrm farmhouse home with an impressive front porch and many trees. This Boutique horse property offers 3 Priefert stalls in a shed row facing a sturdy fenced pasture and a pole barn with electricity. Horses can access a stock pond and a pipe-hitching post to prepare for the riding ring. You can enjoy nature on the back deck while watching your horses roam. The open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area is perfect for entertaining a gathering. The home also features a large primary bedroom with an ensuite bath and outside deck access, a small office, an XL jetted tub, and a separate shower in the bathroom. Two generous-sized bedrooms and a hall bath with a shower complete the home. Two separate garages, one could be a shop. There are also several local equestrian facilities nearby.
